DevContainer integration in IntelliJ is in alpha state, but as soon it becomes better, we should make sure that we can use the team's DevContainer in that IDE, too.

It is also not possible to use an Alpine image as base image in the Dockerfile, but we can generate it nevertheless and connect to it via {{docker exec}}:
{code}
 docker exec -it "$(docker container ls --all --filter=ancestor=jb-devcontainer-devops --format ".ID")" /bin/bash
{code}
